subject: Re: Big Fan Here - Let's Collaborate!
description_text:
Hi Simsonn Team,


Following up on my previous email about collaborating on some content. Let
me know if you’re interested I want to start filming this series soon so
content can be posted promoting local LA spots over the busy holiday season.


Talk soon,
Annika

@Electricmodel (55,000 Tiktok followers)

conversations.body_text: Hi Annika,     Thank you for reaching out — we’re really excited about the possibility of working with you! However, it seems we haven’t received your previous email regarding the collaboration details.  Could you please resend your proposal or share a brief outline of your content plan? We’d love to review it and explore how we can work together on this project.  Looking forward to your reply!   Best regards, The Simsonn Team
